## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **enfortumab vedotin Padcev 2019** = first FDA nectin-4 ADC mUC. 2023 EV-302 1L EV+pembro chemo-free 패러다임 변경. cisplatin-gemcitabine 30+ year backbone 종료. quantum-VQE 의 nectin-4 + MMAE linker 결합 fit.
2. **EV+pembrolizumab EV-302 2023** = first FDA 1L mUC chemo-free regimen. 평균 OS 31.5mo vs cisplatin-gem 16.1mo doubling. 만성 paradigm shift.
3. **erdafitinib Balversa 2019 + 2024 expansion** = first FDA FGFR3/2-altered mUC. 2024 broader expansion. FGFR3 mutation 20% mUC + 70% NMIBC. quantum-VQE 의 FGFR3 selective pocket fit.
4. **nadofaragene firadenovec Adstiladrin 2022** = first FDA gene therapy NMIBC. IFN-α2b adenovirus intravesical. BCG-unresponsive 적응증. cross-gene_therapy_platform.
5. **nogapendekin alfa inbakicept-pmln Anktiva 2024** = first FDA IL-15RaR-α-IL-15 fusion + BCG. NMIBC BCG-unresponsive 새로운 cytokine fusion paradigm. quantum-VQE 의 IL-15Ra-IL-15 interface fit.
6. **BCG intravesical 50+ year** = mycobacterial live attenuated NMIBC 1L. cross-tropical_ntd mycobacteria origin 흥미. global BCG shortage 2017-현재 = supply issue. Anktiva + BCG 2024 = revival.
7. **mitomycin gel Jelmyto 2020** = first FDA UTUC nephron-sparing low-grade. reverse-thermal gel 으로 ureter dwell-time 확보. quantum-VQE limited (formulation 중심).
8. **5-IO atezo/pembro/nivo/avelumab/durva 2017-2020** = bladder 가 melanoma/lung 외 IO 5-mAb 폭발적 첫 적응증. atezolizumab 2017 platinum-ineligible 1L = first FDA IO bladder. avelumab 2020 maintenance JAVELIN-100 unique.
9. **sacituzumab govitecan Trodelvy 2021** = TROP2 ADC mUC. EV MMAE 와 다른 SN-38 linker. cross-adc 2 ADC class.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, bladder cancer specific 임상 의미 한정.

